# =====================================================================
# CriterIA — .dockerignore raíz (contexto = raíz del monorepo)
# =====================================================================
# Aplica a builds donde el contexto es el repo completo:
#   - servicio `criteria-api` en Railway (Root Directory vacío)
#   - servicio `etherpad` en Railway (Root Directory vacío)
#   - `docker compose build` desde nelai-pwa/ (context: ..)
#
# nelai-pwa/.dockerignore queda como respaldo si alguien construye con
# contexto = nelai-pwa/ directamente.

# --- Git / workspace ---
.git
.gitignore
.github
.vscode
.idea
.cursor
.DS_Store

# --- Artefactos de build / dependencias (se reconstruyen) ---
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/dev-dist
**/build
**/.yarn/cache
**/.yarn/install-state.gz
**/.yarn/unplugged
**/.yarn/build-state.yml
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# --- Secretos y locales ---
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/.certs
nelai-pwa/etherpad/APIKEY.txt

# --- Logs ---
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*

# --- Tests / coverage ---
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output
**/*.map

# --- Dockerfiles del propio repo (no necesarios dentro de la imagen) ---
**/Dockerfile
**/.dockerignore
**/docker-compose*.yml
**/docker-compose*.yaml
**/railway.json
